{"id": "1468021347715387606", "channel_id": "1436097679653601340", "type": 0, "author_id": "672881215841501203", "author_name": "zzz1pp3rr", "author_bot": false, "content": "Tbh I never felt like there was any anniversary - there was no real anni event (character selector and 200 pulls are just afk tabs for me), and raid, although was nice in terms of rewards - is just lazy copy-paste of previous iteration. \nTLDR: rewards and rotational banners are nice, ani event is non existent.", "timestamp": "2026-02-02T23:12:43.813000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1468023306375528520", "channel_id": "1436097679653601340", "type": 0, "author_id": "219084432198336522", "author_name": "armyofthalia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Coming from Mihoyo gacha games, seeing so many pulls given during anniversary was a shocker. The one day banners were also incredible thing to see and I would love to see other flash banners in the future for other special occasions. That being said, it did feel like there wasn't any real event besides the login banners which was a bit of a disappointment but at the same time, I just started playing so I had plenty of things to do in the meantime but I feel it would feel much more different if I was a more enfranchised player", "timestamp": "2026-02-02T23:20:30.794000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🆙", "emoji_id": null, "count": 20}, {"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
